title: I Got Cancelled Again AGAIN - Off The Rails #31
description: Today we go over the controversy surrounding Monday's episode. We also cover notorious pick-up artist Cobra Tate being arrested, an on-field report from DJ Khaled's Hollywood Walk of Fame Star Ceremony, and the longest Jordan Peterson impression in the history of the planet.
